{"tid":1040186,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去郵輪假期遲大到 船長唔理自私情侶直接開走","createTime":"2019-02-28T02:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T09:41:20.000Z","uid":28366,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6cc5d6f1281dffb5e2b7f0d0fbafd09d818431d9","tid":1040186,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7g4mPa8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7g4mPa8.png&h=bdf30397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外國一對情侶參加郵輪假期時只顧自己遊覽，在開船時間過了45分鐘後仍未現身，當郵輪準備離港時才抵達碼頭，最後船長及船員沒有理會他倆揮手叫停，直接開郵輪離開。<br />\n<br />\n片段攝於本月15日，一架停泊在巴哈馬拿騷島（Nassau）的美國皇家加勒比（Royal Caribbean）郵輪準備開走，拍片人指郵輪發出的最後登船時間是3時半，在過了45分鐘後就準備離港。<br />\n<br />\n然而在4時20分左右，一對情侶乘客才施施然現身，他們拿着購物袋向郵輪揮手，希望可獲准上船。片段拍到他倆多次揮手示意自己未上船，又走向船尾與船員大聲理論，但船員拒絕為他們停船，郵輪慢慢駛離岸邊出發。<br />\n<br />\n據悉這是7天郵輪旅程的第6天，是郵輪停港的最後一站，之後將返回美國邁阿密（Miami）。該對情侶如要由當地改乘飛機返回邁阿密，一張單程機票約為180美元（約1400港元）。<br />\n<br />\n網民也指摘該對情侶稱：「討厭不跟約定時間的人」、「下次戴隻好一點的手錶」，但也有人替他們不值，「這種行程安排是我永遠也不乘坐郵輪的原因，你只有很少時間遊覽，他們想你留在船上花費」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190228/59308037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190228%2F59308037&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td62paxXJRTFpYESBXKIXFX0%3D&h=83408fca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190228%2F59308037&h=af205df0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190228/59308037</a>"},{"pid":"86177504f36b9a5761cb1d2793b6a853fc5f46f8","tid":1040186,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"除咗抵死都唔知講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0286492b708864bd49314dc9302f5b7d59c937b2","tid":1040186,"uid":122134,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:32:12.000Z","msg":"抵<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ElUyD1ZfcSU/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FElUyD1ZfcSU%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=3efa6e67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9345c5591b2f65065b534a0a7dc709b0f9dfe8b3","tid":1040186,"uid":46527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:33:51.000Z","msg":"幾千人就兩個咩"},{"pid":"a934a75798793e65bb1d7c5732083f1b9cb74810","tid":1040186,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:39:32.000Z","msg":"抵"},{"pid":"dafd17c0a91aeb490b770590cd01945d676658f8","tid":1040186,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06fde154301cc9759e07e25c9aacf0a8e789d6d","tid":1040186,"uid":163801,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但也有人替他們不值，「這種行程安排是我永遠也不乘坐郵輪的原因，你只有很少時間遊覽，他們想你留在船上花費」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你知係咁就咪搭啦!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班飛機幾點?? 唔好遲到喎!! 飛機都唔等人㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb3332dc3e456c31e2dd732a5071a1a5829adc0","tid":1040186,"uid":46042,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:47:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=weFR6UDcr3w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DweFR6UDcr3w%C5%92LIHKG%C5%92&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td62paxXJRTFpYESBXKIXFX0%3D&h=947422ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=weFR6UDcr3w</a><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=weFR6UDcr3w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.